name: Extraterrestrial (SephoWepho)
description:
Created SOLO in two weeks for Clover Jam 2! Horror-ish janky game set in fake realities and SPACE that you'll hopefully have fun with!

Audio: Chosen and edited by me, but derived from royalty free Youtube videos

Palette: https://lospec.com/palette-list/comicscapes-50

Inspired by: Outer Wilds - Echoes of the Eye, Little Nightmares, and others like them

Controls: WASD to move and interact, Mouse and Click for flashlight (late game)

EXTRA IMPORTANT!!!! CURRENT VERSION IS BROKEN AND WILL CONSISTENTLY SOFTLOCK YOU!!! I have a post-jam patch on Gamejolt along with the web version, but when rating, remember THE GAME SHOULD'VE BROKEN AFTER THE SECOND LEVEL!

Patched/Web version: https://gamejolt.com/games/extraterrestrial/801615
